title: Episode 263: Pretty...but Gangsta (Feat. Saucy Santana)
itunes:title: Episode 263: Pretty...but Gangsta (Feat. Saucy Santana)
description:
Rapper, Saucy Santana joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his new album “Pretty Little Gangsta” and things get crazy quickly! Saucy opens up about his car getting shot up after a night out, being accused of touching children at a local pool, and much more. Enjoy!
